{"tid":88261,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"｛學神｝考車","createTime":"2017-01-20T13:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T04:11:39.000Z","uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac74516b11fe01e8b7350a825bc3bf3a4ffcbbb8","tid":88261,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以3波停車<br />\n有時前面綠燈無車，行緊35km/h到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦啦紅燈就一定要3波停<br />\n<br />\n但師傅話唔好，最好係入2波。<br />\n我都過聽師傅講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但想知考試3波停係咪就係一個細tick?<br />\n停得唔好就fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a168dda8cbd3a3b591d724b6d1aa66199a1643d0","tid":88261,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可唔可以3波停車<br />\n有時前面綠燈無車，行緊35km/h到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦啦紅燈就一定要3波停<br />\n<br />\n但師傅話唔好，最好係入2波。<br />\n我都過聽師傅講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但想知考試3波停係咪就係一個細tick?<br />\n停得唔好就fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你練開都知大概個燈位時間架啦"},{"pid":"7ee47a5aff7aa067b23d51cd4ff254e9617eeec2","tid":88261,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"除非急煞，否則2波停車。<br />\n<br />\n你冇理由唔知燈位"},{"pid":"0934f1575d79b9fc408a670e41f98e0aa811c3f9","tid":88261,"uid":58006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"師傅話唔可以<br />\n但有朋友試圖急煞就可以，不過你急煞得都通常fail <br />\n自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57fee55b1545513a6ad22201649ebe703753b56","tid":88261,"uid":58006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師傅話唔可以<br />\n但有朋友試圖急煞就可以，不過你急煞得都通常fail <br />\n自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596e6b73fd6f925dbb76a034335da6b7cc61c580","tid":88261,"uid":16390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T19:08:27.000Z","msg":"三波停車好似一定肥<br />\n你最好燈位前4個車位到收油<br />\n佢轉燈就轉波收哂<br />\n唔轉就比油去埋佢<br />\n咁樣一定無死"},{"pid":"7decc70fb21c78b570181c5873da4811c75dbc0f","tid":88261,"uid":17470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T19:09:07.000Z","msg":"叫你入2波係當你未停定又轉翻燈都可以即刻行<br />\n突然轉燈咁一係就繼續行 一係局住3波停"},{"pid":"b9dffe241e45557dc85a78734c45afb20283e648","tid":88261,"uid":24513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"不明文規定 好似係唔得"},{"pid":"831214811906be63edc981a9526bf9e44c1341f5","tid":88261,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T23:37:27.000Z","msg":"停唔切係因為你望得唔夠遠<br />\n判斷唔到前面情況<br />\n你又唔係70，80標出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9160e8c267eefab1e45f7598dfb2f9caafc7e0","tid":88261,"uid":21414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T00:47:23.000Z","msg":"真實揸車你4停都得<br />\n考車要拖落2波停車，否則有機會剔你波段不當"},{"pid":"1de5a06ff0264f51ae011a2ccaef2d20444862cc","tid":88261,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"考車果陣過燈位幾大都拖二波先過<br />\n考車慢唔緊要（當然唔好慢得太離譜）<br />\n快唔會有人讚你<br />\n唔需要搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88a0eed6857745c7e77fc67cea40133ef946881","tid":88261,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"一定要二波停<br />\n一波起步<br />\n過燈尾 班馬線 就落定二波無死"},{"pid":"ca43357a0a5d5cae4ee0960bf98282b004c72cdd","tid":88261,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T19:44:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8820d309a5daed4996e46b092143636875de5505","tid":88261,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T20:00:34.000Z","msg":"揸車要望遠啲<br />\n你離遠望到有燈位<br />\n開始收油唔好咁快<br />\n差唔多到係綠燈就踩返油過咗佢<br />\n差唔多到係黃燈就落波收油停車"},{"pid":"1644dfbaa1411b9c857f5bbe0b1d1991a6ab4dd0","tid":88261,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"予其你3波停 就不如比油過埋燈位<br />\n3波停一係停得好chok,一係出白線,已經fail<br />\n考試自己係比油過埋，1 take pass"},{"pid":"628ba40a26961f7d5e129e7ca2f2a7f9c843f662","tid":88261,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"其實一定做到二波停嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即使好長直路都好 你係果到學過大約都會記得盞燈綠幾耐<br />\n你一定要望遠啲 盡量早啲望到佢係咩燈<br />\n如果你距離佢好遠既時候佢綠緊<br />\n我會建議你唔好快 夠力上三波就keep住埋去<br />\n咁既速度你印一印brake即刻轉二波吊極力子 架車會收得好快 好快就可以停到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將近到都仲係綠就踩快啲 咁點都唔會衝到紅燈 頂多黃燈<br />\n離遠紅燈唔使講啦 準備停車<br />\n如果離遠見到佢準備轉綠就要靠你平時記憶決定過唔過到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n參考下好啦 最好都係問番你師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}